articles.title: Australian Open: Madison Keys upsets Iga Swiatek and will face Aryna Sabalenka in the final - The Associated Press
articles.description: Madison Keys saved a match point and upset No. 2 Iga Swiatek 5-7, 6-1, 7-6 (10-8) in a high-intensity Australian Open semifinal to reach a Grand Slam title match for the second time in her career. Keys is a 29-year-old American who was the runner-up at the 20…
